# ############################################################################
# CODEOWNERS — write-scope guard for high-leverage paths.
#
# Goal: prevent doc/canon drift from passing-by edits. Every PR that touches
# the paths below requires review from the listed owners. The rest of the
# repo has no required owner (default branch protection still applies).
#
# Replace the placeholder logins below with real GitHub handles before
# enabling "Require review from Code Owners" in branch protection.
# ############################################################################

# ----- Root-level source-of-truth files -----
/MANIFEST.md                 @lead
/.github/CODEOWNERS          @lead
/.pre-commit-config.yaml     @lead

# ----- GRACE methodology canon (rare, intentional changes only) -----
/docs/GRACE_CANON.md         @lead
/grace/canon/                @lead
/grace/README.md             @lead

# ----- Project documentation (numbered docs + manifest) -----
/docs/MANIFEST.md            @lead @reviewer
/docs/README_*.md            @lead @reviewer
/docs/0[0-9]_*.md            @lead @reviewer
/docs/1[0-9]_*.md            @lead @reviewer
/docs/DEPLOY.md              @lead @reviewer

# ----- Controller packets (waves) -----
/grace/packets/              @lead @reviewer

# ----- Contract source of truth (Pydantic) and generated TS -----
/apps/api/app/schemas/       @lead @reviewer
/packages/contracts/         @lead @reviewer

# ----- Marker / drift / manifest gates -----
/scripts/grace_lint.py       @lead
/scripts/grace/              @lead
/scripts/contracts/          @lead
